name: Urban Gourmet
overview:
Urban Gourmet was founded in 1999 by Anne and David Doughty derived from their passion of good food, seamless events and superb dining experiences. Anne and David took from their 25 years of experience in the function, wedding and corporate catering industry to create a catering company dedicated to serving delicious food while maintaining uncompromising standards.

The Urban Gourmet is committed to delivering outstanding food and events with personality, elegance and flair. Urban Gourmet has an extensive catering venue selection throughout Auckland ranging from iconic landmarks such as the Auckland Museum to intimate boats and marquees. Urban Gourmet offers a range of mouth-watering food selections for seated dinners, weddings, buffets, corporate catering, event catering, cocktail parties and more.

Whether clients are looking to serve delectable canapés, hot or cold fork favourites or a full catered meal, Urban Gourmet promises to satisfy their taste buds as well as meet aesthetic and professional standards. When catering all events from wedding to corporate Urban Gourmet assures it will be well-organised and stress-free. Urban Gourmet believes that every detail counts and will help clients through the whole event process from selecting the perfect venue and choosing the best complimentary wine to arranging the necessary equipment and staff.
